<title>BELGIUM: SCHERING-PLOUGH TO INVEST $31 MLN IN BELGIUM.</title>
<headline>SCHERING-PLOUGH TO INVEST $31 MLN IN BELGIUM.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1996-12-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>U.S. pharmaceuticals firm Schering-Plough Corp said on Tuesday it would invest one billion francs ($31.2 million) to modernise its Belgian production unit in the town of Heist-op-den-Berg.</p>
<p>&quot;The production unit of Schering-Plough in Heist-op-den- Berg has become the most important of the international group...the drugs produced here are exported to over 86 countries,&quot; Schering-Plough Benelux said in a statement.</p>
<p>-- Brussels Newsroom +32 2 287 6810, Fax +32 2 230 7710</p>
